high_descs: Turn around to your right then face the counter with bowl and other things
Pick up the bowl on the counter
Turn to your right and walk towards the fridge
Open the fridge put in and out the bowl then close the fridge
Turn to your left move forward then turn to your right head to the shelves on your right
Put the bowl on the shelves
anns.task_desc: Put the cold bowl on the shelves

high_descs: Turn around from facing the sink to face the counter with the bowl on it.
Pick up the bowl from the counter.
Turn to your right and walk to the fridge.

Open the fridge door and place the bowl to the right of the loaf of bread on the shelf directly above the crisper drawers, close the fridge door; after cooling, open the fridge door, pick up the bowl, close the fridge door.
Turn to your left and walk toward the door in your line of sight, hang a left and walk to the brown shelf to the left of the recycling bin.
Place the bowl on the third shelf from the bottom to the right of the stainless steel decanter.
anns.task_desc: Pick up a bowl, refrigerate it, place it on a shelf

high_descs: Turn around and face the counter behind.
Pick the bowl up from the counter.
Go to the right and stand in front of the fridge.
Put the bowl in the fridge and shut the door, then open the door and grab the bowl.
Turn and cross the room to face the brown shelves.
Put the bowl on the brown shelf.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled bowl on a shelf.
